1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,760
What happened?

4
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,519
Doctor.

5
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,359
What's wrong with my mom?

6
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,079
Uremia.

7
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:29,959
Surgery can't wait.

8
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,560
Uremia.

9
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,560
It's okay. I'm here.

10
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,920
Is it early or late stage?

11
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,719
Early stage.

12
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:45,480
What's the cure rate?

13
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,040
The main issue right now

14
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:49,480
is not about the cure rate.

15
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,560
It's about the kidney donor.

16
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,120
It's okay.

17
00:01:58,079 --> 00:02:00,680
I'll handle the kidney donor issue.

18
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,959
Mr. Song, we've found a caregiver.

19
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,800
She meets all your requirements.

20
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:10,759
How much?

21
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,840
500 per day.

22
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,039
I'll pay her an extra 300.

23
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,039
Tell her to say
it's 200 per day to Ji Xuan.

24
00:02:17,479 --> 00:02:18,000
Understood.

25
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:34,360
Mr. Song, thank you for today.

26
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,800
Feeling better now?

27
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,360
A little better.

28
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:39,280
Good.

29
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,319
Then let's talk about work.

30
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:44,560
The revised proposal
has been sent to your email.

31
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,919
That's not what I meant.

32
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,039
Why did you join Wansheng back then?

33
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,960
For the money.
Wansheng offered a high salary.

34
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,000
Song Group can offer more than Wansheng.

35
00:02:59,080 --> 00:02:59,639
Join us?

36
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,879
I appreciate the offer, Mr. Song.

37
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,360
But I'm not considering
a job change right now.

38
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,080
Why?

39
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,719
Mr. Song.

40
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:16,199
Things beyond money can never be repaid.

41
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,919
I don't want to complicate my life.

42
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,680
Ji Xuan.

43
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:29,159
Cracks in life let the light shine in.

44
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,360
Don't be so wary of me.

45
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:34,439
I may not be a gentleman,
but I'm no villain.

46
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:38,120
We've been looking to enter
the real estate market in recent years.

47
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:40,919
But I've been lacking someone reliable.

48
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:45,800
Women and power.
I lean toward the latter.

49
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,680
I hope you'll reconsider.

50
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,199
And tell me then.

51
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,199
Mom, you're awake.

52
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,800
Feeling any better?

53
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,600
Mom, don't worry.

54
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:45,879
The doctor told me.

55
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:48,920
Your illness isn't serious.
It can be cured.

56
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:55,120
Xuan, I can't burden you anymore.

57
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,879
If it weren't for this family, for me,

58
00:04:58,639 --> 00:05:02,480
with your abilities,
you wouldn't be living like this.

59
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,560
Listen to me.

60
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,240
My illness. I'm not treating it.

61
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:09,959
Keep this money and live well.

62
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,360
Mom.

63
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,079
Have you ever thought?

64
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,720
Without you,

65
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,720
how would I live?

66
00:05:49,204 --> 00:05:50,996
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

67
00:05:51,156 --> 00:05:53,036
♪Flickering neon lights♪

68
00:05:53,236 --> 00:05:56,564
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

69
00:05:57,076 --> 00:05:59,348
♪Every star is♪

70
00:05:59,636 --> 00:06:03,508
♪My heartbeat for you♪

71
00:06:04,820 --> 00:06:06,644
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

72
00:06:06,688 --> 00:06:08,356
♪And land in your arms♪

73
00:06:08,576 --> 00:06:12,212
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

74
00:06:12,468 --> 00:06:15,028
♪In the blue sky♪

75
00:06:15,092 --> 00:06:19,220
♪Your smile still lingers♪

76
00:06:20,148 --> 00:06:23,796
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

77
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,680
(Song Group can offer
more than Wansheng.)

78
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,759
Join us?

79
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:32,199
We've been looking to enter
the real estate market in recent years.

80
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,120
But I've been lacking someone reliable.

81
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,840
Women and power.
I lean toward the latter.

82
00:06:41,504 --> 00:06:42,839
(I hope you'll reconsider.)

83
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,240
(And tell me then.)

84
00:06:45,204 --> 00:06:47,264
♪How I wish I could give you♪

85
00:06:47,508 --> 00:06:51,276
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

86
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:55,084
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

87
00:06:55,168 --> 00:06:57,152
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

88
00:06:57,348 --> 00:07:02,348
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

89
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,240
Need something?

90
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:39,759
Come in.

91
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,680
Have a seat.

92
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,160
Mr. Song.

93
00:08:16,839 --> 00:08:18,519
I'm here to confirm something.

94
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,439
Confirm what?

95
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:23,399
Are you trying to keep me or hire me?

96
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,000
Hire.

97
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,879
Thank you, Mr. Song.

98
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:48,840
I'm willing to join Song Group.

99
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:49,799
Welcome.

100
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:53,559
I won't bother you
any longer. I'll head out.

101
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,200
It's pouring outside. I'll drive you.

102
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:03,240
Mr. Song, given
our superior-subordinate relationship,

103
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,879
your behavior is a bit inappropriate.

104
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,639
I think, given
our superior-subordinate relationship,

105
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,879
the way you're speaking is improper.

106
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,440
Put it on.

107
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,320
No need, Mr. Song.

108
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,080
Take a week off.

109
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:31,440
I'll handle things
with Wansheng for you.

110
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:32,960
Thank you, Mr. Song.

111
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:34,679
No need for thanks.

112
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,360
I'm a businessman.
I don't do deals at a loss.

113
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:40,120
If you want to thank me,
show it through actions.

114
00:09:50,336 --> 00:09:50,600
(Song Group)

115
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:53,200
Ji Xuan,
the newly appointed project manager.

116
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:57,080
Mr. Song, does
the chairman know about this?

117
00:09:57,279 --> 00:10:00,120
Does a manager's appointment
need the chairman's approval?

118
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,320
Department heads, report on your work.

119
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,080
Grandpa, what brings you here?

120
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:12,919
Chairman, please have a seat.

121
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:14,639
All sit.

122
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,159
Continue.

123
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,679
Marketing Department.

124
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,519
Bisheng owns a plot of land
in a prime location in the city.

125
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:25,840
But it's been sitting idle
for some reason.

126
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:29,240
If we can purchase
this land from Mr. Yu,

127
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:32,399
we can maximize its value.

128
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:35,840
Mr. Yu of Bisheng is an overseas Chinese
who lives abroad year-round.

129
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,879
Very few have seen him in Qingcheng.

130
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:41,159
Mr. Yu returns to Qingcheng
every year at this time.

131
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,519
This is an opportunity.

132
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,679
You sure you can track his whereabouts?

133
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,960
Of course not.

134
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:51,919
But haven't we just hired
a capable project manager?

135
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:58,799
Ji Xuan will handle this project.

136
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,279
Yes.

137
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:03,440
Strength is the best way to open doors.

138
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:07,840
Ji Xuan, you have
one month to prove yourself.

139
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,399
This project is difficult.

140
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,808
If she pulls it off,

141
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,600
just keeping her job is...

142
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,360
What do you plan to do?

143
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,440
Clear accountability.

144
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,799
If Ji Xuan succeeds,

145
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,639
give her a one percent commission.

146
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:22,399
And if she fails?

147
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,799
If she fails,

148
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:31,360
it will be the last time
we see Miss Ji in the company.

